# Functional programming paradigm

/*

	Data 		---> Don't Modify the data
				     in the same location
	Functions 	---> Pass function as para.
	(1st-Class)		     Return as Value
				     Store in variable
	Pure 		---> Don't Modify the state 
	Functions
	Recursion 	---> Function call itself
				     (loops|Control Structure)
	Lazy Evaluation	---> Expression in function Parameters
			     Evaluated only on usage
	---------
		Other Ideas
*/

